{"comments":"ExtractedElement → Element Converter\n\nThis is the dual parser bridge: Foundry scrapes pixels into ExtractedElement\n(Schema atoms), this module converts to Element, and Element renders to any\ntarget (Halogen, Static HTML, WebGPU).\n\n## The Dual Parser Architecture\n\n```\nFoundry (any visual source)\n        ↓\nExtractedElement (Schema atoms: OKLCH, Pixel, FontWeight...)\n        ↓  fromExtracted\nElement msg (universal IR)\n        ↓\n  ┌─────┴─────┬────────────┐\n  ↓           ↓            ↓\nHalogen    Static      WebGPU/GL\n HTML       HTML       DrawCommand\n```\n\n**Same atoms → Same Element → Same output. Every user. Every time.**\n\n## Design Principles\n\n1. **Schema atoms are the truth**: All visual properties come from bounded,\n   typed Schema atoms. No CSS parsing, no string manipulation.\n\n2. **Pure transformation**: ExtractedElement in, Element out. No effects.\n\n3. **Recursive structure**: ExtractedElement trees become Element trees.\n\n4. **GPU-ready**: The resulting Element can flatten to DrawCommands for\n   WebGPU/WebGL/Canvas rendering, not just DOM.\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Render.FromExtracted as FE\nimport Hydrogen.Target.Halogen as TH\nimport Hydrogen.GPU.Flatten as Flatten\n\n-- Scraped data → Element\nelement :: Element Void\nelement = FE.fromExtracted scrapedTree\n\n-- Render to Halogen (web)\nhalogenHtml = TH.toHalogen element\n\n-- Render to GPU (WebGPU/Canvas)\ngpuCommands = Flatten.flatten element\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Convert an ExtractedElement tree to an Element tree.\n\nThe resulting Element has no event handlers (Void message type).\nUse `fromExtractedWithHandlers` if you need to attach handlers.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Scraper","Types"],"ExtractedElement"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element","Types"],"Element"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Void"],"Void"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[109,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/FromExtracted.purs","start":[109,1]},"title":"fromExtracted"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert an ExtractedElement tree with custom event handler injection.\n\nThe handler function receives ExtractedElementData and returns attributes\nto add (typically event handlers based on element ID or class).\n\n```purescript\nfromExtractedWithHandlers \\data ->\n  if data.className == \"clickable\"\n    then [ E.onClick (HandleClick data.elementId) ]\n    else []\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Scraper","Types"],"ExtractedElementData"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element","Types"],"Attribute"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Scraper","Types"],"ExtractedElement"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element","Types"],"Element"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"visibility":"TypeVarInvisible"},"tag":"ForAll"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[127,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/FromExtracted.purs","start":[123,1]},"title":"fromExtractedWithHandlers"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert extracted colors (OKLCH) to Element styles.\n\nOKLCH → RGB → CSS string for browser compatibility.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Scraper","Types"],"ExtractedColor"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element","Types"],"Attribute"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"visibility":"TypeVarInvisible"},"tag":"ForAll"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[204,69],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/FromExtracted.purs","start":[204,1]},"title":"colorStyles"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert extracted typography atoms to Element styles.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Scraper","Types"],"ExtractedTypography"]